But when Councilor Beas brought up, Vice President Beas brought up this proposal, for someone that's at the beginning, totally was so for charter review, the need for charter review was so important, it was one of my top three initiatives.

126
00:15:01,493 --> 00:15:27,369
But as I started seeing the process of the mayor's office with different commissions and different processes and the way the budget was not being presented, I could show you, I could share the writings when she ran for mayor, how disgusted she was that not having a budget that the city council can work together with the city administration and how disgusted she was.

127
00:15:27,590 --> 00:15:30,672
And that was the first initiative was to transparency in the budget.

128
