159
00:18:38,648 --> 00:18:47,453
I think that these amendments get at I think this is no surprise to anybody in this room, they get at the things that we that give us the most consternation on the Council all of the time.

160
00:18:48,334 --> 00:18:51,656
The fact that we need independent legal counsel to support our legislative work.

161
00:18:52,156 --> 00:18:57,259
