164
00:19:13,723 --> 00:19:21,524
Some of these priorities are universally shared, others of them, you know, some of us feel more strongly about than others, but the fact is we're a legislative body and it's really hard for us to legislate.

165
00:19:22,644 --> 00:19:26,785
