176
00:20:11,590 --> 00:20:13,391
It's not about a specific administration.

177
00:20:14,751 --> 00:20:27,758
Through these, you know, and perhaps they'll change a little bit as we're going through subcommittee, as we bring them back to committee of the whole, the council could have a more real involvement in the budget that gets passed, not just essentially be asked to be a rubber stamp, though, of course, nobody would ever put it that way.

178
00:20:27,858 --> 00:20:31,640
But when you look at the process, it's hard not to draw that conclusion.

179
